msgid ""
"Assumes that the file is an archive in a format that :py:mod:`shutil` has an "
"unpacker for. The arguments ``extract_dir`` and ``format`` are passed "
"directly on to :py:func:`shutil.unpack_archive`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../src/py/pyodide/http/_pyfetch.py:docstring of
#: pyodide.http._pyfetch.FetchResponse.unpack_archive:8
