"directory is used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../src/py/pyodide/http/_pyfetch.py:docstring of
#: pyodide.http._pyfetch.FetchResponse.unpack_archive:11
msgid ""
"The archive format: one of ``\"zip\"``, ``\"tar\"``, ``\"gztar\"``, "
"``\"bztar\"``. Or any other format registered with :py:func:`shutil."
"register_unpack_format`. If not provided, :py:meth:`unpack_archive` will use "
"the archive file name extension and see if an unpacker was registered for "
"that extension. In case none is found, a :py:exc:`ValueError` is raised."
msgstr ""

